INFORMATION MANAGEMENT. 4TH REPORT ON THE ACTIVITIES OF THE COMMITTEE FOR
INFORMATION AND DOCUMENTATION ON SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY OF THE EUROPEAN
COMMUNITIES (1978-80).

THE FIRST 3 REPORTS OF THE COMMITTEE ARE AVAILABLE AS EUR 5177, EUR 5597 AND
